snippet: The Jets are left with the rookie starter Geno Smith and the backup Matt Simms as the only healthy quarterbacks for the season opener Sunday.
abstract: NFL Roundup; New York Jets release backup quarterback Brady Quinn; other football news noted.
lead_paragraph: The Jets are left with the rookie starter Geno Smith and the backup Matt Simms as the only healthy quarterbacks for the season opener Sunday.

headline.main: Jets Cut Quinn, Leaving Two Healthy Quarterbacks, but Will Probably Re-Sign Him
